      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an exceptional 2002 BMW M3 (E46), featuring the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine and a tactile Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox. This specimen is in concours-level condition, with the individual throttle bodies (ITBs) perfectly synchronized and the dual-VANOS system recently overhauled for optimal variable valve timing. The chassis remains rigid with documented rear subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein dampers and Turner Motorsport bushings. Power is delivered through a tight variable M-differential, ensuring peak lateral grip and exit speeds. The factory paint retains its original depth with zero swirl marks, and the interior is free of the typical bolster fatigue found in lesser examples. This is a mechanically sorted, collector-grade driver\u2019s car with a comprehensive service dossier.",
